055/063: Then which of the Blessings of your Lord will you both (jinns and men) deny?
055/064: Dark green (in colour).
055/065: Then which of the Blessings of your Lord will you both (jinns and men) deny?
055/066: In them (both) will be two springs gushing forth water.
